      <section name='staff'>

         <para number='1' comment='Turn back non-staff - loc 325'>
         You walk towards the airlock, but it remains closed. You press the access button, but nothing happens; even pulling on the manual emergency lever has no effect. Very puzzling! Then you spot a notice tacked crookedly onto the airlock door: "Access to Brass is restricted due to emergency maintenance. No admittance without authorisation." That explains it.
         </para>

